{
  "stem": "935.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I couldn't be fenced in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was only one gate-- the gate you came in through, a big, huge iron gate, where two of those horrendous tall Belgian guards stood.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Otherwise, it was like a military kasein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was some--so many entrances, and each entrance had, on their second floor, left and right, for about I would say 500, 600 people, sleeping accommodation downstairs in the first floor.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was a house.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was really a kasein, a house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was not barracks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm sure that once upon a time, they were used by military.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And all you had was a courtyard-- stones-- around that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You couldn't see over the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have no idea what was on the outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Whether we were smack in the middle of the city, or whether we were on the outskirts, I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, I couldn't have you told you then.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was no dining room, there was no recreation room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were only these-- what you'd call-- pigeon holes, our sleeping quarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I mean, like this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "No room for storing anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You had to, whatever, do as best as you can.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Toilets was a catastrophe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There were two, outside on the hall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Men and women were together, couples were together, families were together, lovers or not lovers were together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a [NON-ENGLISH]-- in other words, one was in charge of each of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It what his job to see that there were no fights, no arguments, no thievery going on, no lovemaking against somebody's will, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Food-- well, you know, if it is your first encounter with being imprisoned, everything is horrible.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Looking back on it a few months later, it was heaven, because there were no guards' chambers there.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
